title: VA Indie Easy Rock NOV 2013 - Strangers (Dutch Treat I2 HQ)
description:
Hi, already the fourth playlist of November 2013 and after listening all other playlists of the recent days, you are probably ready for some really good stuff, not the hard kind but the nice one. A Playlist you can actually listen to (if your taste lets you). I miss that sometimes with my friend's - more or less random ordered - lists.... Enjoy,
